item.title: Digital Crime Scene Investigations
item.description: Tue, Jan 28, 6:00 PM to 9:00 PM Location: Nederlands Forensisch Instituut Ever wondered what the life of a digital crime scene investigator looks like? Step into the world of the NFI this evening and experience a live criminal case where your digital forensics skills will be required! This meetup is organised by the Dutch Forensics Institute. Curious what it’s like to work at NFI? You will hear experience from two kick-ass ladies!
